        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s tabulation of colonists curious but explicable.</p>
            <p>Working on Tasmanian flora; contemplating general essay on Australian distribution: Tasmania and Australia same alpine species; Swan River flora very peculiar and quite distinct from New South Wales.</p>
            <p>Trying to establish new journal at Linnean.</p>
